{"tid":2354576,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中 TG 後罵「 X 你老母死差佬」 中年漢上訴得直 法官：支持警者在某情況下罵警 非互相矛盾","createTime":"2021-01-05T14:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T15:05:16.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bce9fde911a091fa1b4bd28de78a70ef82b58c18","tid":2354576,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"網民前年 11 月 10 日發起「八區開花」，中年漢被指在旺角指罵警方「X 你老母，死差佬，我頭先無喇喇食咗兩個催淚彈」。他否認一項在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序行為罪，經審訊後裁定罪成，判處 200 小時社會服務令。他不服定罪向高院提上訴，法官黃崇厚早前裁定他上訴得直，定罪撤銷，今（5 日）頒下判詞。法官黃崇厚指，原審裁&zwj;判&zwj;官陳慧敏對上&zwj;訴&zwj;人的誠信判斷，其中一&zwj;項理由建基於不準確的事實，「對定罪裁決是否穩妥感到不安，認為在這情況下，確認定罪會有不公」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD-tg-%E5%BE%8C%E7%BD%B5-x-%E4%BD%A0%E8%80%81%E6%AF%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%B7%AE%E4%BD%AC-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E5%BE%97%E7%9B%B4-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E8%80%85%E5%9C%A8%E6%9F%90%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E4%B8%8B%E7%BD%B5%E8%AD%A6-%E9%9D%9E%E4%BA%92%E7%9B%B8%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD-tg-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25BD%25B5-x-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%2580%2581%25E6%25AF%258D%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E4%25BD%25AC-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%25BE%2597%25E7%259B%25B4-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%259F%2590%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%259D%259E%25E4%25BA%2592%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%259F%259B%25E7%259B%25BE%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGwVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=67928991\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD-tg-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25BD%25B5-x-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%2580%2581%25E6%25AF%258D%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E4%25BD%25AC-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%